headline: Prediction: 2 Stocks That Will Be Worth More Than Medical Properties Trust 3 Years From Now
summary: Medical Properties Trust is deeply out of favor because of a dividend cut.  Prologis and Rexford Industrial are out of favor because of tariff concerns.  Prologis and Rexford have better prospects than Medical Properties Trust.
